spec_data.Name: python2-weakrefmethod
spec_data.Description:
Python 3.4 include a ``WeakMethod`` class, for storing bound methods using weak
references
(see the `Python weakref module
<http://docs.python.org/library/weakref.html>`_).

This project is a backport of the WeakMethod class, and tests, for Python 2.6.
The tests require the `unittest2 package
<http://pypi.python.org/pypi/unittest2>`_.
